<!--
================================================
Header Component

Purpose:
This file contains the navigation bar that will
appear on multiple pages.

Why use a partial?

Instead of repeating the same HTML in every
page, we create reusable components.

Later if we update navigation, we change it
in one place.

This concept is similar to reusable components
in React.
================================================
-->

